game.name: Fishing King
game.description:
Fishing can be more funny and rewarding than you thought of! We have got you covered with a brand new adventure game where you have to trap fishes by shooting your cannon. Are you ready friends to accept this unique kind of challenge? Join King Fishing and be prepared to grab as many fishes as you can to earn money! There are dozens of cannon combinations and multiple fishes to collect. You would have tremendous amounts of fun and endless challenges to explore. 

Catch the bigger fishes as well to improve your fishing abilities in this HTML5 fishing game! You will have the full freedom to set the size of your net to grab more fishes at a time. Remember you also have to cost you more coins for each shot. So try to aim your target carefully to save your coins and use them for the right purpose. Do not forget to purchase power-ups and upgrades to catch bigger kinds of fish.

Keep fishing until you catch the large and most fast fish out there! Track your level by looking at the top left corner of the screen in this cool endless fishing challenge! Grab your weapon and get ready to travel around this wonderful aquatic world that is full of colorful fishes and treasures! Catch them using a fishnet, prepare your own team of fishes and let the world show that you are the biggest fish master on this planet! Good luck to end this fishing adventure on a good note! Have fun in our other free adventure games in multiple devices without download!
